{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration suitable for face verification use cases."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"simple","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Configuration","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/FaceAutoCaptureViewController\/Configuration-swift.class","preciseIdentifier":"s:11DotFaceCore0B25AutoCaptureViewControllerC13ConfigurationC"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component operates without any visual aids or guidance for the user, with the exception of the detection layer (tracking circle).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"There is no automatic triggering of the capture process.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Instead, the client is responsible for initiating the capture by explicitly calling the ","type":"text"},{"code":"requestCapture","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This configuration provides a minimalistic approach, offering flexibility to the client in managing the capture timing and user interaction,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which is often desired in verification scenarios.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore","doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/FaceAutoCaptureViewController","doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/FaceAutoCaptureViewController\/Configuration-swift.class","do